data.description: SELLER IS MOTIVATED AND SELLING FOR UNDER MARKET VALUE AND WILL OFFER $5000 TOWARDS BUYERS RATE BUY DOWN !Welcome  to the heart of Pinellas County, where this four-bedroom home awaits you! This stunning home has been completely updated with all the modern amenities you could ever need. As you step inside, you'll notice the brand new white solid cabinetry with soft close doors, granite countertops, and a beautiful glass tile backsplash that perfectly complements the new stainless steel appliances. The bathrooms have also been recently remodeled with porcelain tile, and the home features new interior doors, ceiling fans, and fresh interior paint. The home has been upgraded with new waterproof Luxury vinyl flooring that is both stylish and practical. The roof, air-conditioning, windows, garage door, and are all just a few years old, ensuring that you won't have to worry about any major repairs for years to come. Situated on a large corner lot, this home boasts two storage sheds, an outdoor patio perfect for entertaining guests, and a white vinyl fence that surrounds the property. With plenty of room to store a boat or an RV, you'll never have to worry about parking again. Another great feature of this home is the gas generator that is wired to the power, which will run your kitchen, living room, and master bedroom in the event of a power outage. This feature ensures that you'll always be prepared, no matter what the weather throws your way. If you are looking for a home close to the beaches for a SHORT TERM RENTAL the city or Largo is one of few cities within pinellas county that allows them so if you're looking for a large home as an investment you have got to see this! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning home yours! Come take a look today and see all that it has to offer.
